node.text:
“Monsters are real!!!! It took awhile, but he eventually came my way. My heart was pounding as I slowly raised my spear. Big thanks to @daniel_townsend for inviting me to come down. An experience I’ll never forget!

I hunted this guy with @townsendandsons on private property. They are a nuisance around south Florida, eating livestock, fawns, & numerous pets. All the meat from the back of the neck to the tip of the tail from this monster reptile is edible & delicious. “
